" I believe that I could change the odds a bit if you'lltrust me to 
get the results you want. As you have probably noticed I tend to have 
a certain influencial quality." Phobia could practically predict 
Klusters response but he wanted Kluster to believe that he couldn't 
be predicted. "If you will allow me to leave for the remainder of the 
week I'll show results. At the end of the week I'll return, as our 
agreement says, to assist your assult stratagy on the Iron Fist." A 
silent dramatic pause filled the room "With my scans, and your 
leadership abilities how can we fail?"
